    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Hemolysis index comparison and pressure rise validation both include structured UQ. The velocity field PIV validation result characterizes inherent PIV measurement variability qualitatively; this does not affect the primary RH acceptance decision. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the COU1 regulatory submission decision.",
